text: "Im tiknikn es" (, ) is a song by Armenian singer Lilit Hovhannisyan and child singer Nanul. The song was written by Vahram Petrosyan, with production handled by the "DUETRO" Studio. It was released as a single on March 9, 2015. It has more than 43 million views on YouTube. Director was Artyom Abovyan, who was also the cameraman. ==References== ==External links== * * musixmatch lyrics Category:2015 singles Category:Lilit Hovhannisyan songs Category:Dance- pop songs Category:2015 songs Category: Armenian songs
